The paper deals with the problem of deriving closed-form maximum average rate for real-time distributed control in 5G networks, which requires reliable communication links. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper may also be relevant to the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories, as these fields often involve real-time control and communication in distributed systems.
